# docs/skills-catalog/**/SKILL.md is published as a GitHub Release asset and
# its sha256 (in docs/skills-catalog/skills-catalog.json) is verified both at
# CI-publish time and at app fetch time (lib/skill-catalog.ts). Windows
# checkouts with core.autocrlf=true silently convert LF -> CRLF in the working
# tree, which changes the file's bytes (and therefore its hash) relative to
# the LF blob Linux CI actually checks out -- force LF here so the hash is the
# same on every OS.
docs/skills-catalog/**/SKILL.md text eol=lf
docs/skills-catalog/skills-catalog.json text eol=lf
